Start the Game: Run the script in your terminal using python filename.py.

Set the Rounds: Enter the number of rounds you want to play when prompted.

Choose Your Move: For each round, type your choice using the name or the number:

1 for Rock

2 for Paper

3 for Scissors

Check the Results: The computer will reveal its move, and the game will announce the winner of the round.

Handle Ties: If you and the computer choose the same move, the round repeats until someone wins.

Win the Match: The game tracks the score and crowns the overall winner once all rounds are finished.
